# https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The two regions are completely disconnected (there are no common pieces)."@en .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/dc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "disconnected"@en .
# 
# https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "the boundaries of the regions touch, but their interiors are disjoint"@en .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "externally connected"@en .
# 
# https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "two regions have the same spatial extent"@en .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/eq> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "equal"@en .
# 
# https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntppi> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "the first region is entirely inside the second region and their boundaries do not touch"@en .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "non-tangential proper part"@en .
# 
# https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntppi
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/ntppi> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
