<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/tpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://purl.org/region/rcc8/Region> .
<https://purl.org/region/rcc8/tpp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "the first region is entirely inside the second region and their boundaries touch each other from the inside"@en .
